Marshall's dad is convinced if we have an outdoor wedding in New York,

33
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:32,100
他会被抢劫，所以要改在室内
he's going to get mugged, so it's going to be inside now.

34
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:36,800
