It'll be great. We're still going to have our acoustic guitar player.

35
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,600
[婚礼前3个月] 所以不用原音吉他
So now, instead of an acoustic guitar,

36
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:41,400
要改用竖琴
we're having a harp player.

37
