老兄，我可不打算去数那清单有几张
Dude, I'm not gonna count how many pages the list is.

41
00:01:54,700 --> 00:01:56,100
我不是笨蛋
I'm not crass.

42
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,900
无论如何，那无所谓，因为她怀孕了
Well, it doesn't matter anyway. She's pregnant.

43
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:01,100
太好了！我可以划掉两个项目
Sweet! I can cross off two things.

44
