He kind of did.

95
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,800
那就是Scooter
That's Scooter.

96
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:19,300
你的高中男友，Scooter？
Your high school boyfriend, Scooter?

97
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:20,900
他的真名叫Bill
His real name is Bill.

98
