It's not "Scooter" anymore.

116
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,100
叫我Bill
It's Bill.

117
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,700
我变了很多，Lily
A lot of things have changed about me, Lily,

118
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,000
