but one hasn't.

119
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,800
我还是爱着你
I still love you.

120
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:03,100
我来这里就是要赢回你的心
And I came here to win you back.

121
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,800
你真是可爱，哦，不，是真的吗？
You're really cute. Oh, no. Really?

122
