只有挑染是，其余是我搞的 很抱歉，宝贝
Just the frosted tips. I did the rest. I'm sorry, baby.

345
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:32,300
我把个整个婚礼都毁了，是吧？
I've ruined the whole wedding, haven't I?

346
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:34,600
哦，不，你没有毁了婚礼，宝贝
Oh, no, you didn't ruin the wedding, sweetie.

347
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,100
它早就毁了
It was already ruined.

348
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,900
没有花，没有摄影师
There's no flowers, no photographer.

349
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,800
还有，Scooter也在这
Oh, and Scooter's here, by the way.

350
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:40,700
我知道，我听说了
Yeah, I know. I heard.

351
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:43,800
我的面纱被弄得乱七八糟 那个竖琴手在生孩子
My veil got thrashed, the harp player is in labor,

352
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:46,000
而我没有穿着我的婚礼内衣
and I'm not wearing my wedding underwear.

353
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:48,600
什么？ 没有后面写着"Marshall的财产"那件？
What? No "Property of Marshall" across the back?

354
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:50,700
那人家怎么知道那是谁的屁股？
How are people going to know whose butt that is?

355
00:15:50,800 --> 00:15:52,500
怎么了？
What happened?

356
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:57,500
记得我们本来想要的婚礼 是秘密的户外婚礼吗？
Remember the wedding we wanted, the intimate outdoor ceremony?

357
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:59,400
真希望我们能办那样的婚礼
I wish we could have that wedding.

358
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,400
那就办啊
So do it.

359
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:04,300
什么？
What?

360
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:05,800
现在就结婚
Get married now.

361
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,200
就在这
Right here.

362
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:09,700
听我说，这里不就是你们想要的户外
Look, it's outside like you always wanted.

363
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,800
只有亲密的朋友
Intimate, close friends.

364
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:14,400
没有吉它，但很接近了
There's no guitar, but it's pretty close.

365
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:16,300
Barney可以主持仪式
Barney can officiate.

366
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:20,200
对，我可以
Yes. Yes, I can.

367
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:23,600
抱歉了各位，你们全都掉了样东西：
Uh, excuse me, guys. You all dropped something:

368
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:24,900
你们的下巴--
your jaws--

369
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:29,500
因为Barney Stinson就要做 一场婚礼的共犯
because Barney Stinson is about to aid and abet a marriage.

370
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:33,000
我们可以这么做吗？ 那在那里的那些人怎么办？
Could we even do that? I mean, what about all those people in there?

371
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:35,200
那边也办，然后要是出了什么状况
Do that one, too. And then when everything goes wrong,

372
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:38,200
你们就不会在意 因为真正的婚礼在这里办过了
you won't care because you already had the real wedding out here.

373
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:41,700
你怎么想，宝贝？
What do you think, baby?

374
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,700
我喜欢这个主意
I love it.

375
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,000
我也是
Me, too.

376
00:16:45,100 --> 00:16:48,100
就这么做吧，让我们在结婚前结婚
Let's do it. Let's get married before we get married.

377
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,500
太好了
Great.

378
00:16:49,800 --> 00:16:51,500
等等
Wait, hold on.

379
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:54,600
抱歉打扰一下，先生
Excuse me, sir.

380
00:16:54,700 --> 00:16:56,800
我们可以借一下你的帽子吗？
Could we borrow your hat?

381
00:16:58,100 --> 00:16:59,000
好的
Okay.

382
00:16:59,100 --> 00:17:00,400
谢谢你
Thank you.

383
00:17:08,700 --> 00:17:09,800
帽子
Hat.

384
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:12,400
我们在想到帽子之前
We thought of authentic Native American headdress

385
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,600
竟会先想到了"有认证的美洲原住民头饰"
before we thought of hat.

386
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:18,100
谢谢各位光临
Thank you all for coming.

387
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:21,900
怕在座有人不认识我...
For those of you who don't know me...

388
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:25,300
我并不是那种很相信婚姻的人
I'm not the biggest believer in marriage.

389
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:31,900
但是... 你们在一起真的很棒
But... you two are so great together, you know?

390
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:39,900
就好像，你们是为彼此而存在
It's like you were, uh, made for each other.

391
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:42,200
- 他要哭了 - 不，才没有
- He's gonna cry. - No, I'm not.

392
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:49,700
我没有，我没有，我没有...
I'm not, I'm not, I'm not, I'm not, I'm not.

393
00:17:55,500 --> 00:17:57,000
Lily和Marshall...
Lily and Marshall...

394
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:00,800
当大家看到你们，他们...
when everyone sees you, they...

395
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,000
看见的是真爱
see true love.

396
00:18:05,700 --> 00:18:07,400
最美的爱...
It's the best love...

397
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:15,800
我们可以... 直接跳到交换戒指之类的吗？
Can we just, um, move on to the rings or something?

398
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:20,400
不好了
Oh, no.

399
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:22,900
我没有带我的誓辞
I don't have my vows.

400
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,400
我也没有带我的
I don't have mine either.

401
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:27,900
你们不需要誓辞 只要说说为什么爱他/她
You don't need your vows. Just say why you love each other.

402
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:32,000
好，我先
Okay, I'll go first.

403
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:35,700
Lily
Lily,

404
00:18:36,500 --> 00:18:39,200
我爱你有一百万种理由
there are a million reasons why I love you.

405
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,500
你让我笑
You make me laugh

406
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:44,300
当我生病时照顾我
and you take care of me when I'm sick.

407
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:49,400
你贴心，关心 甚至做了一道鸡蛋菜肴以我命名
You're sweet, caring and you even created an egg dish and named it after me.

408
00:18:49,500 --> 00:18:52,200
她在炒松蛋之前，放了些意式沙拉酱在里面
She puts a little Italian dressing in scrambled eggs before she cooks them.

409
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:54,900
叫作"Marshall蛋"，而且那棒极了
It's called "Eggs Marshall," and it's awesome.

410
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:59,400
但我爱你最主要的理由是
But the main reason that I love you is

411
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:01,400
你是我最好的朋友，Lily
that you're my best friend, Lily.

412
00:19:01,600 --> 00:19:04,500
你是... 我有过最好的朋友
You're, uh... you're the best friend I ever had.

413
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,600
- 抱歉了，兄弟 - 没问题
- I'm sorry, buddy. - No problem.

414
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:07,900
完全没关系
It's totally okay.

415
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,500
轮到我了
My turn.

416
00:19:10,900 --> 00:19:12,400
哦，谢谢你
Oh, thank you.

417
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:18,200
Marshall，我爱你，因为你很有趣
Marshall, I love you because you're funny

418
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,900
你让我感到被爱
and you make me feel loved

419
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,700
让我感到安全
and you make me feel safe

420
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:27,400
而为了我们的周年纪念 你送了我一件汗衫，上面写点
and for our anniversary you gave me a sweatshirt that says,

421
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:30,800
"Lily和Marshall天下无双，自'96年开始"
"Lily and Marshall. Rockin' It Since '96."

422
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,900
我有点希望现在我是穿着它的
I kinda wish I was wearing it right now

423
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:37,000
因为那有你的味道
'cause it smells like you.

424
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:41,000
但我爱你最主要的理由 Marshall Ericksen
But the main reason I love you, Marshall Ericksen,

425
00:19:41,100 --> 00:19:44,100
是你让我快乐
is you make me happy.

426
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,800
你总是让我快乐
You make me happy all the time.

427
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:53,600
嘿，我找到你的内裤了
Hey, I found your panties!

428
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:55,700
我没关系
I'm good.

429
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,500
Marshall，你愿意接受Lily成为你的妻子
Marshall, do you take Lily to be your wife to have and to hold from this day forward?

430
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:01,400
- 慢一点 - 我没办法
- Slow down. - I can't.

431
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:03,400
由今日起互相扶持，直到人生最后一天？
From this day forward so as long as you both shall live?

432
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,400
我愿意
I do.

433
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:08,000
Lily，你答应Marshall成为你的丈夫 并互相扶持... 一天？
Lily, do you promise to take Marshall to be your husband to have and to hold... live?

434
00:20:08,100 --> 00:20:08,800
我愿意
I do.

435
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:10,100
好，那么
Okay, then,

436
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:14,200
以在Lafayette街的法院工作的 那个超刻薄的老巴基斯坦人
by the power invested in me by the very bitter old Pakistani man

437
00:20:14,300 --> 00:20:16,800
所授予我的权力
who works down at the courthouse on Lafayette Street,

438
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:20,200
我现在宣布你们成为夫妻
I now pronounce you man and wife.

439
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,100
你可以亲吻新娘了
You may kiss the bride.

440
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:31,500
- 你抽烟吗？ - 不
- Do you smoke? - No.

441
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:35,100
哇，婚姻中的第一个谎言 还真是快
Wow. First lie of marriage. That was fast.

442
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:40,100
之后，我们都回到里面第二个婚礼
After that, we all went back inside for the second wedding.

443
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:42,200
而且，的确是有很多事情出错
And yes, a lot of things did go wrong,

444
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:43,300
但那都没有关系
but it didn't matter

445
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:45,600
因为当我回头看那一天
because when I look back on that day,

446
00:20:45,700 --> 00:20:47,600
我所记得的就是第一个婚礼
what I remember is the first wedding;

447
00:20:47,700 --> 00:20:49,700
那个私密的户外婚礼
the intimate outdoor ceremony

448
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:51,500
只有一些亲密的朋友在场
with just close friends

449
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:53,500
和一支原音吉他
and an acoustic guitar.

450
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:08,100
你觉得如何？
How do you feel?

451
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:11,300
好累，我今天结了两次婚
Tired. I got married twice today.

452
00:21:15,300 --> 00:21:18,100
那我们第一次以已婚夫妻的身份做爱 你想在哪里呢？
So where do you want to do it for the first time as a married couple,

453
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:21,000
是舒适的饭店房间 还是接待大厅的厕所？
nice hotel room or a reception hall bathroom?

454
00:21:21,100 --> 00:21:22,500
你怎么想？
What do you think?

455
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,600
当然是厕所
Bathroom, of course.

456
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,200
拜托不要
Please don't.

457
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,300
- 抱歉，Ted - 抱歉，Ted
- Sorry, Ted. - Sorry, Ted.

458
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,200
老爸老妈的浪漫史 第二季第二十一集 译者：Bug Li

